data.description: Why wait to build when you can own this beautiful Holiday Builders 2022 Foxtail floorplan? Located on a corner lot w/3 bedrooms, 2 baths & a 2 car garage. Kitchen has white cabinetry, stainless appliances & opens to great room w/Indian River Pecan Tree mantle & electric fireplace below. LR (or flex room) & DR up front off foyer. Outback you'll find a 14x10 Cordova Gazebo w/power & an 8x6 Utility shed. Laundry room inside. Garage has epoxy flooring & an additional 240-volt outlet. No HOA. Barber Street Sports Complex just down the street! sizes approx-subj to error.
